data_description: Seed mass data for Sydney species
notes: needs reprocessing before going into AUSTRAITS because the data did not include useful seed mass measurements
primary_source: Previously unshared dataset from Leishman, M. R., Westoby, M., & Jurado, E. (1995). Correlates of seed size variation: a comparison among five temperate floras. Journal of Ecology, 83: 517-529.
